maintext:
Winning numbers drawn in ‘All or Nothing Evening’ game
AUSTIN, Texas (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday afternoon’s drawing of the Texas Lottery’s “All or Nothing Evening” game were:
04-06-09-10-12-14-15-17-18-19-20-24
(four, six, nine, ten, twelve, fourteen, fifteen, seventeen, eighteen, nineteen, twenty, twenty-four)
